# Analytics Layer Summary

| View Name              | Business Purpose                                                                               |
| ---------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| dim_passengers         | Customer analytics, passenger profiling, loyalty segmentation, and booking behavior analysis.  |
| dim_employees          | Workforce analytics, employee segmentation, and operational staffing insights.                 |
| fact_booking           | Booking trends, customer purchasing behavior, loyalty analysis, and revenue contribution.      |
| fact_flight            | Flight operations monitoring, route analysis, aircraft utilization, and performance reporting. |
